    {
      "id": "25",
      "name": "更多訊息",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "textual_research",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "artifactPos": "",
                "audios": [],
                "desc": "<p>協會認證牌手提米。今天也在等待父親歸來的男孩…在所有悲傷的思緒襲上心頭之前，還是先用有趣的牌局與美麗的鴿子短暫轉移自己的視線吧。</p>",
                "id": "更多訊息56587",
                "img": "",
                "title": "地圖文本"
              },
              {
                "artifactPos": "",
                "audios": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">派蒙：</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">在最近的旅行裡，你有沒有什麼留下深刻印象的人呢？</span><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">派蒙：</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">我的話，應該是莎拉吧。</span><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">旅行者：</span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">提米。</span><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">派蒙：</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">欸！為什麼？</span><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">旅行者：</span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">最近每次吃甜甜花釀雞，都會想到他的臉…肉也變得難吃了。</span></p>",
                "id": "更多訊息1454",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/16/84496276/917e8e67944b52c28db451b8a2c6e89c_498152912751926091.png",
                "title": "旅行者：關於印象最深刻的人…"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
